OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day with long sunny
OL,6,Fspells and increasingly strong
OL,7,Feasterly winds, with coastal gales
OL,8,Flikely. Patchy cloud possible later in
OL,9,Fthe day. Warm inland but cooler along
OL,10,Feastern coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry evening with some late
OL,13,Fsunny spells and a little patchy
OL,14,Fcloud, though remaining windy. A
OL,15,Fmostly clear night will follow,
OL,16,Fbecoming cool with a brisk breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
