OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAnother day of long sunny
OL,6,Fspells. Windy, though less so inland
OL,7,Fthan on Wednesday, with strongest
OL,8,Fwinds near coasts. Warm, but feeling
OL,9,Fcooler in exposed areas and along
OL,10,Feastern coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FFriday,
OL,13,Fpatchy cloud and sunny intervals, very
OL,14,Fwarm, chance of showers. Cloudy
OL,15,FSaturday and Sunday, risk of rain or
OL,16,Fshowers, sometimes heavy. Cooler with
OL,17,Fgenerally light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
